name: zacian_crowned_sword
pokemon_entry: Known as a legendary hero, this Pokémon absorbs metal particles, transforming them into a weapon it uses to battle.

name: zamazenta_crowned_sword
pokemon_entry: In times past, it worked together with a king of the people to save the Galar region. It absorbs metal that it then uses in battle.

name: galarian_meowth
pokemon_entry: It loves to collect shiny things. If it's in a good mood, it might even let its Trainer have a look at its hoard of treasures.

name: galarian_ponyta
pokemon_entry: It can't run properly when it's newly born. As it races around with others of its kind, its legs grow stronger.

name: galarian_rapidash
pokemon_entry: This Pokémon can be seen galloping through fields at speeds of up to 150 mph, its fiery mane fluttering in the wind.

name: galarian_slowpoke
pokemon_entry: Slow-witted and oblivious, this Pokémon won't feel any pain if its tail gets eaten. It won't notice when its tail grows back, either.

name: galarian_slowbro
pokemon_entry: Slowpoke became Slowbro when a Shellder bit on to its tail. Sweet flavors seeping from the tail make the Shellder feel as if its life is a dream.

name: galarian_farfetchd
pokemon_entry: The stalk this Pokémon carries in its wings serves as a sword to cut down opponents. In a dire situation, the stalk can also serve as food.

name: galarian_weezing
pokemon_entry: It mixes gases between its two bodies. It's said that these Pokémon were seen all over the Galar region back in the day.

name: galarian_mr_mime
pokemon_entry: The broadness of its hands may be no coincidenceâmany scientists believe its palms became enlarged specifically for pantomiming.

name: galarian_slowking
pokemon_entry: Miraculously, this former Slowpoke's latent intelligence was drawn out when Shellder poison raced through its brain.

name: galarian_corsola
pokemon_entry: It will regrow any branches that break off its head. People keep particularly beautiful Corsola branches as charms to promote safe childbirth.

name: galarian_zigzagoon
pokemon_entry: It marks its territory by rubbing its bristly fur on trees. This variety of Zigzagoon is friendlier and calmer than the kind native to Galar.

name: galarian_linoone
pokemon_entry: Its fur is strong and supple. Shaving brushes made with shed Linoone hairs are highly prized.

name: galarian_darumaka
pokemon_entry: It derives its power from fire burning inside its body. If the fire dwindles, this Pokémon will immediately fall asleep.

name: galarian_darmanitan
pokemon_entry: The thick arms of this hot-blooded Pokémon can deliver punches capable of obliterating a dump truck.

name: galarian_darmanitan
pokemon_entry: The thick arms of this hot-blooded Pokémon can deliver punches capable of obliterating a dump truck.

name: galarian_yamask
pokemon_entry: It wanders through ruins by night, carrying a mask that's said to have been the face it had when it was still human.
